ed on the estimated tag positions from the previous\nstep. Theoretical analysis and simulation results show that the proposed\nERBL-EDMC method effectively solves the RBL problem with incomplete\nmeasurements. It obtains the optimal positioning results while maintaining low\ncomputational complexity compared with the existing RBL methods based on\nsemi-definite relaxation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 16:20:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-24"}
